In the Matter of T.E.F. No. 608A04. Supreme Court of North Carolina. February 22, 2005. Judith Tillman, Assistant Attorney General, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 22nd day of February 2005 by Appellee for Extension of Time to File Brief:

"Eleven day extension allowed. Appellee shall have up to and including the 14th day of March 2005 to file and serve his/her brief with this Court. By order of the Court in conference this the 22nd day of February 2005."
